com.soctec.soctec.network

Class NetworkHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soctec.soctec.network.NetworkHandler

  • public class NetworkHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles all network-related tasks. Can handle both server and peer connections. Returns data to MainActivity via runOnUiThread()
    Version:
    5.2
    Author:
    David Johnsson

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      private class  NetworkHandler.ActiveThread
      This thread can connect to a peer, exchange data, and send it to MainActivity
      private class  NetworkHandler.PassiveThread
      This thread listens for a connection, exchanges data, and sends it to MainActivity
      private class  NetworkHandler.ServerThread
      This thread can connect to the server and a) push data to it, or b) fetch data from it.
